@startuml Kasir_Konversi_Stok_Sequence
title Sequence Diagram - Kasir: Konversi Stok

actor Kasir
participant "UI" as UI
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "Service" as Service
participant "DB" as DB

Kasir -> UI: Buka menu konversi stok
UI -> Controller: GET konversi-stok
Controller -> DB: Ambil data produk
DB --> Controller
Controller --> UI: Tampilkan form

Kasir -> UI: Input data konversi
UI -> Controller: Submit form
Controller -> Service: Proses konversi

Service -> DB: Mulai transaksi
Service -> DB: Validasi & update stok
Service -> DB: Simpan data konversi
DB --> Service: Commit

Service --> Controller: Berhasil
Controller --> UI: Tampilkan konfirmasi
Kasir <-- UI: Lihat hasil konversi

Kasir -> UI: Cetak struk (opsional)
UI -> UI: Kirim ke printer

Kasir -> UI: Konversi lagi atau keluar
@enduml
